  "texts": [
    "Further Discussion Related Entities Filtering usingPrompt-based LLM Previously, the selection of related companies from the named entity recognition (NER) output was performed manually.",
    "Although this method allows direct human oversight, it is time-consuming, subjective, and may not scale well when applied to larger datasets.",
    "To address these limitations, an alternative approach involves using promptbased large language models (LLMs) to automate the company filtering process.",
    "By designing appropriate prompts, LLMs can intelligently identify and extract relevant company entities from unstructured text, reducing the need for manual intervention while improving consistency and scalability.",
    "This LLM-based method offers a more systematic and adaptable solution, especially in scenarios where the number of entities is large or continuously evolving."
  ],
